Dataset_field.sql_query: select user_id from tbl_users where user_login = '{UserContext.sid}'
select group_name from tbl_groups where group_id = (select group_id from tbl_groupmembers where user_id = '{UserContext.userid}')
select group_concat(queue_id) from tbl_queue_members where object_id = '{UserContext.userid}' and object_type = 0
SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(REPLACE(queue_name,'SP_','')) FROM tbl_queues WHERE queue_name like 'SP_%' AND FIND_IN_SET (queue_id, '{UserContext.userQueues}') <> 0

SELECT CONCAT('', '', GROUP_CONCAT(orderedTable.results SEPARATOR ''), '
Package AMCN ID (PR.ID)TitleSource Asset IDPlatformPress SheetMedia StatusArtwork StatusDelivery Date
') FROM ( SELECT CONCAT( '',IFNULL(mainTable.AMCNID,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.Title,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.sourceID,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.DeliveryPlatform,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.PressSheetStatus,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.mediaStatus,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.artStatus,''),'', '',IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(mainTable.DeliveryDateCalc, '%m/%d/%y'),''),'' ) results FROM ( ( SELECT [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] AMCNID, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Title] Title, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.DeliveryPlatform] DeliveryPlatform, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.DeliveryDate] DeliveryDate, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.ArtworkOffset] ArtworkDueDate, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.PORTAL_SendDate] DeliveryDateCalc, placement.source sourceID, IF( touch.mediaStatus IS NULL, IF( placement.amcnid IS NULL, 'Not Requested', IF( placement.sourceStatus='Ready for Distribution', 'In Progress', 'Requested' ) ), touch.mediaStatus ) mediaStatus, IF( COUNT([ADAM_Record_Component.ComponentType])=0, 'Not Requested', IF( COUNT([ADAM_Record_Component.ComponentType]) = SUM(IF([ADAM_Record_Component.FileStatus] = 'Ready for Distribution',1,0)), 'Ready for Distribution', IF( SUM(IF([ADAM_Record_Component.PortalRecordStatus] IS NOT NULL,1,0)) = 0, 'Requested', 'In Progress' ) ) ) artStatus, IF( vam.obj IS NULL, 'Not Created', IF( GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT IF([ADAM_NL_Component.FileStatus]='','X',[ADAM_NL_Component.FileStatus]) SEPARATOR '')='Ready for Distribution', 'Ready for Distribution', 'In Progress' ) ) metaStatus, IF( [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Inactive]='true', 'Cancelled', IF( IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Revoked],'') = 'Revoked', [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Revoked], IF( IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered],'') IN ('Accepted','Rejected'), [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered], IF( IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered],'') = 'Delivered', [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered], IF( IFNULL(a.description,'')='', IF( LOWER([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.PlacementSEND]) = 'new', IFNULL(NULLIF([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.ValidityStatus],''),'New'), IFNULL(vam.PlacementSEND,IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.PlacementSEND],'')) ), IF( -- Awaiting Ack Metadata delivered to Vampire a.def_id = 94439, 'Metadata Sent to Vampire', IF( -- Awaiting Vampire Completion a.def_id = 95362, 'Metadata Received by Vampire', IF( -- Awaiting Ack Legacy Update a.def_id = 104398, 'Update IDs', a.description ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) Status, CASE WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'No Press Sheet' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'No Press Sheet' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] = 'No Press Sheet' THEN 'No Press Sheets' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] like 'Migrated%' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] like 'Migrated%' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] like 'Migrated%' THEN 'Migrated - Needs Checking' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'New' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'New' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] like 'New' THEN 'New' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'In Progress' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'In Progress' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] = 'In Progress' THEN 'In Progress' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'Press Ready' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'Press Ready' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] = 'Press Ready' THEN 'Press Ready' ELSE 'In Progress' END AS PressSheetStatus FROM [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery] -- Join to Deliveries to get only the latest instance INNER JOIN ( SELECT MIN(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery] GROUP BY [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] ) maxID ON maxID.obj = [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery].object_id -- JOIN to components (of delivery) for artwork status LEFT JOIN [ADAM_Record_Component] ON [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery].object_id = [ADAM_Record_Component].object_id AND [ADAM_Record_Component.ComponentType] = 'Artwork' -- Join to Vampire version of Deliveries to get the current state in Vampire flow LEFT JOIN ( SELECT object_id obj, [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] amcnid, [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.PORTAL_SendDate] senddate, [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.PlacementSEND] PlacementSEND FROM [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery] -- INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery] -- GROUP BY [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID])maxID ON maxID.obj = [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery].object_id ) vam ON vam.amcnid = [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] -- Join to activities to get current state of Vampire flow LEFT JOIN tbl_bpm_activities a ON a.process_id = vam.obj AND a.status = 'active' -- Join to placements table to get the state of the placement LEFT JOIN ( SELECT object_id obj, [ADAM_Record_Placement.AMCNID] amcnid, [ADAM_Record_Placement.HierarchyParentID] hpid, [ADAM_Record_Placement.SourceID] source, [ADAM_Record_Placement.SourceMediaAssetStatus] sourceStatus FROM [ADAM_Record_Placement] INNER JOIN ( SELECT MAX(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_Record_Placement] GROUP BY [ADAM_Record_Placement.AMCNID] ) maxPub ON maxPub.obj = object_id ) placement ON placement.amcnid = [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.HierarchyParentID] -- Join to touchpoints placement table to get the state of the placement LEFT JOIN ( SELECT [ADAM_Touchpoint_Component.HierarchyParentID] amcnid, [ADAM_Touchpoint_Component.FileStatus] mediaStatus FROM [ADAM_Touchpoint_Component] INNER JOIN ( SELECT MAX(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_Touchpoint_Placement] GROUP BY [ADAM_Touchpoint_Placement.AMCNID] Next Day') OR ([AVAILS_Transmission.Prototype] = 'EST - Store Front Opening (Short Form)')) AND ( [AVAILS_Episode.Platform] <> 'Amazon EST')) THEN 'Next Day TV' ELSE '' END LicenseRightsDescription, '' FormatProfile, '' HDR, '' WCG, '' HFR, '' NGAudio, [AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] StartDateTimeFrom, 'Open' StartDateTimeTo, '' PriceType, '' PriceValue, '' PriceCurrency, '' SRP, '' Description, '' OtherTerms, '' OtherInstructions, '' TitleID , '' EditID, [AVAILS_Episode.exportAMCNID] AltID, [AVAILS_Episode.exportAMCNID] ContentID, '' AvailID, '' UV_ID, '' DMA_ID, '' ReportingID, '' Metadata, [AVAILS_Episode.exportAMCNID] ALID, '' SuppressionLiftDate, '' SpecialPreOrderFulfillDate, '' AnnounceDate, [AVAILS_Episode.ReleaseYear] ReleaseYear, '' ReleaseHistoryOriginal, '' ReleaseHistoryPhysicalHV, '' ExceptionFlag, '' RatingSystem, '' RatingValue, '' RatingReason, '' RentalDuration, '' WatchDuration, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.ClosedCaptionsYN] = 'true' THEN 'Yes' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.ClosedCaptionsYN] = 'false' THEN 'No' else '' END CaptionIncluded, '' CaptionExemption, '' Any, '' ContractID, [AVAILS_Episode.ServiceProvider] ServiceProvider from [AVAILS_Episode] LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON ( [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] and [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id={PROCESS::ID} ) LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode_Titles] ON ([AVAILS_Episode_Titles].object_id={PROCESS::ID} and [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode_Titles.AMCNID]) LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM] ON ( [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] and [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM].object_id={PROCESS::ID} ) where ([AVAILS_Episode].object_id={PROCESS::ID} and [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType]='Movie') group by [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID])results ON results.joinval = format.joinval
ORDER BY results.ALID
SELECT [EST_Export_Content_Type.ContentType_ID] as ContentType_ID, [EST_Export_Content_Type.ContentType_Name] as ContentType_Name FROM [EST_Export_Content_Type]

SELECT IFNULL([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles.Title],'') AS Title, IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(CAST([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] AS DATE),'%Y-%d-%m'),'') as LaunchDate, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE [AVAILS_Episode.EpisodeNumber] END AS EpisodeNumber, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE TRIM(LEADING '0' from IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.SeasonNumber],'')) END AS SeasonNumber, IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.corePlatform],[AVAILS_Episode.Platform]) as corePlatform, IFNULL([AVAILS_Transmission.TransmissionTerritory],'') as territory FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id=[AVAILS_Episode].object_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
LEFT JOIN [EST_EXport_data_tmp] ON [EST_EXport_data_tmp].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] IN ('Episode','Program') AND [EST_EXport_data_tmp.exportType] IN ('iTunes Export','SVOD Export') GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission].id
UNION
SELECT IFNULL([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles.Title],'') AS Title, IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(CAST([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] AS DATE),'%Y-%d-%m'),'') as LaunchDate, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE IFNULL(NULLIF([AVAILS_Episode.EpisodeNumber] ,''),'') END AS EpisodeNumber, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE TRIM(LEADING '0' from IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.SeasonNumber],'')) END AS SeasonNumber, IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.corePlatform],[AVAILS_Episode.Platform]) as corePlatform, IFNULL([AVAILS_Transmission.TransmissionTerritory],'') as territory FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id=[AVAILS_Episode].object_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
LEFT JOIN [EST_EXport_data_tmp] ON [EST_EXport_data_tmp].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film') AND [EST_EXport_data_tmp.exportType] IN ('PDS Film Ingest','Vampire Film Ingest') GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission].id
UNION
SELECT IFNULL([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles.Title],'') AS Title, IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(CAST([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] AS DATE),'%Y-%d-%m'),'') as LaunchDate, [AVAILS_Episode.EpisodeNumber] AS EpisodeNumber, TRIM(LEADING '0' from IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.SeasonNumber],'')) AS SeasonNumber, IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.corePlatform],[AVAILS_Episode.Platform]) as corePlatform, IFNULL([AVAILS_Transmission.TransmissionTerritory],'') as territory FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id=[AVAILS_Episode].object_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
LEFT JOIN [EST_EXport_data_tmp] ON [EST_EXport_data_tmp].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Series','Interstitial','Special','Pilot','Digital Series') AND [EST_EXport_data_tmp.exportType] IN ('PDS Series Ingest','Vampire Series Ingest') GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission].id

UPDATE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN ( SELECT [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id as parent_ref_id, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Rating] as rating, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Descriptor] as descriptor, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Reason] as reason, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Content] as content, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.UserCode] as usercode FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
INNER JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID]
INNER JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem] ON [AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
INNER JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film') AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Type]=[AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem.Rating_Type] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.UserCode]=[AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem.Rating_UserCode]
GROUP BY [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id ) AS GROUP_RATINGS ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = GROUP_RATINGS.parent_ref_id SET [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.EpisodeTVRating] = GROUP_RATINGS.rating, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.RatingDescriptorTV] = GROUP_RATINGS.descriptor, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.RatingReason] = GROUP_RATINGS.reason, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.RatingUserCode] = GROUP_RATINGS.usercode
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')
NEW_SQL

	}

					$launchDateTo =  $v_launchDateTo;
					$est = $v_est;
					$SeasonNumber = $v_SeasonNumber;
	}
		
	#Dataset Info
	print DEBUGFILE "\n *** DATASET -> EST_EXport_data_tmp ***\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Platform [" . $platform . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Title [" . $title . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "LaunchDateFrom [" . $launchDateFrom . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "LaunchDateTo [" . $launchDateTo . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Type [" . $type . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "NextDayAfterLinear [" . $est . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Channel [" . $channel . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Territory [" . $territory . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "SeasonNumber [" . $SeasonNumber . "]\n";
	
	#Build the string parameter for URL		
	
	#Remove String from date params
	#( my $launchDateFromParam = $launchDateFrom ) =~ s{^(\d{2})/(\d{2})/(\d{4})$}{$3$2$1};
	#( my $launchDateToParam = $launchDateTo ) =~ s{^(\d{2})/(\d{2})/(\d{4})$}{$3$2$1};
    #$launchDateFrom =~ s{^(\d{2})/(\d{2})/(\d{4})$}{$3$1$2};
	#$launchDateTo =~ s{^(\d{2})/(\d{2})/(\d{4})$}{$3$1$2};
    #print DEBUGFILE "LaunchDateFrom [" . $launchDateFrom . "] new\n";
	#print DEBUGFILE "LaunchDateTo [" . $launchDateTo . "] new\n";
	
	$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$title,"title","&");
	if($launchDateFrom ne "00000000")
      {
        $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$launchDateFrom,"launchDateFrom","&");
      }
    
    if($launchDateTo ne "00000000"){
        $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$launchDateTo,"launchDateTo","&");
    }
	
	#$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,"20200706","launchDateFrom","&");
	#$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,"20210131","launchDateTo","&");
	
	
	#$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,"54051000","publicationSystem","&");
	$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$platform,"publicationSystem","&");
    	
	$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$channel,"channel","&");
	#$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,"491913381538","channel","&");
	
	#$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,"118618010,1269678010","productContents","&");
	$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$type,"productContents","&");
		
	# $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$platform,"platform","&");
	# $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$type,"type","&");
	# $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$est,"est","&");
	# $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$channel,"channel","&");
	# $parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$territory,"territory","&");
	# # remove the last character (&) from parameters string
	
	$parameters = createParamStr($parameters,$SeasonNumber,"seasonNumber","&");
	chop($parameters);
	
	print DEBUGFILE "Parameters [" . $parameters . "]\n";
	
	#for test -- ONLY ACTIVATE THE FOLLOW LINE TO TEST THE REQUEST --
	#$parameters = "launchDateFrom=20200706&launchDateTo=20210131&title=Comic%20Book&publicationSystem=54051000&channel=491913381538&productContents=118618010,1269678010";
    
    
	my $ua = LWP::UserAgent->new;
	#my $url = $config->{host} . $config->{get_updatedRecords_endpoint} . "?launchDateFrom=$launchDateFrom&launchDateTo=$launchDateTo&title=$title&publicationSystem=$platform&channel=$channel&productContents=$type";
	my $url = $config->{host} . $config->{get_updatedRecords_endpoint} . "?" . $parameters;

	print DEBUGFILE "\n" . "Requested URL: " . $url . "\n" . $access_token . "\n";

	my $response = $ua->get($url,'Authorization','Bearer '.$access_token,'x-ibm-client-id',$config->{client_id},'accept','application/xml');

	my $result = undef;
	if ($response->is_success) {
		$result = $response->decoded_content;
		handle_result("SUCCESS",$result);
	}else{
		print DEBUGFILE "\nError in :: Getting Data for Records\n" . $response->status_line . "\n" . $response->decoded_content  . "\n";
		$result = $response->decoded_content;
		handle_err_result("ERROR_GET_DATA_RECORD_RETRIEVAL",$result);
	}
}

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}

sub get_access_token{
        my $config = $_[0];

        my $response = $ua->request(POST $url,[

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	#print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}

		print DEBUGFILE "\nError in :: Getting Data for Records\n" . $response->status_line . "\n" . $response->decoded_content  . "\n";
		$result = $response->decoded_content;
		handle_err_result("ERROR_GET_DATA_RECORD_RETRIEVAL",$result);
	}
}

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	#print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}
